{"id":697,"date":"2024-04-06T22:51:06","date_gmt":"2024-04-06T22:51:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/?page_id=697"},"modified":"2024-05-28T21:45:08","modified_gmt":"2024-05-28T21:45:08","slug":"certification","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/certification\/","title":{"rendered":"CERTIFICATION"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-background-background-color has-background is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-3 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-content-justification-center is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Mes Certifications<\/h2>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-697_9df614-cf .kt-block-spacer{height:6px;}.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-697_9df614-cf .kt-divider{border-top-width:5px;height:1px;border-top-color:#0083ff;width:84%;border-top-style:solid;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-spacer aligncenter kt-block-spacer-697_9df614-cf\"><div class=\"kt-block-spacer kt-block-spacer-halign-center\"><hr class=\"kt-divider\"\/><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Dans le cadre de mon BTS SIO, option SISR, j&rsquo;ai r\u00e9ussi \u00e0 obtenir plusieurs certifications en ligne, cruciales dans le secteur informatique. Ces certifications attestent de mes comp\u00e9tences et connaissances sp\u00e9cifiques, ce qui me conf\u00e8re un avantage notable sur le march\u00e9 de l&#8217;emploi. Elles d\u00e9montrent mon engagement envers mon d\u00e9veloppement professionnel et ma capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 r\u00e9pondre aux besoins techniques actuels.<\/p>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-697_e5cff5-9f .kt-block-spacer{height:6px;}.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-697_e5cff5-9f .kt-divider{border-top-width:5px;height:1px;border-top-color:#0083ff;width:84%;border-top-style:solid;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-spacer aligncenter kt-block-spacer-697_e5cff5-9f\"><div class=\"kt-block-spacer kt-block-spacer-halign-center\"><hr class=\"kt-divider\"\/><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\"><strong>Outil de suivi de formation<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"168\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-947\" style=\"width:302px;height:auto\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"862\" height=\"544\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-963\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-5.png 862w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-5-300x189.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-5-768x485.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 862px) 100vw, 862px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Trello est un outil efficace pour le suivi de formation, permettant de planifier, organiser et suivre facilement les progr\u00e8s et les t\u00e2ches \u00e0 accomplir gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 son interface intuitive et ses fonctionnalit\u00e9s collaboratives.<\/p>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-697_12c0db-bc .kt-block-spacer{height:6px;}.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-697_12c0db-bc .kt-divider{border-top-width:5px;height:1px;border-top-color:#0083ff;width:84%;border-top-style:solid;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-spacer aligncenter kt-block-spacer-697_12c0db-bc\"><div class=\"kt-block-spacer kt-block-spacer-halign-center\"><hr class=\"kt-divider\"\/><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Mes certifications <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">faites<\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp);flex-basis:800px\">\n<h1>Attestation\u00a0<span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">PIX (549 Pix)<\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>La certification PIX m&rsquo;a permis de valider mes comp\u00e9tences num\u00e9riques et informatiques, renfor\u00e7ant ainsi mon profil professionnel dans un monde o\u00f9 la ma\u00eetrise des outils num\u00e9riques est devenue essentielle.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/attestation-pix-20240327.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"247\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_010810500.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-715\" style=\"width:254px;height:auto\"\/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">(Cliquez sur l\u2019image pour le certificat)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;border-radius:0px;box-shadow:none\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp);flex-basis:800px\">\n<h1>Attestation <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">MOOC DE L&rsquo;ANSSI<\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>La participation au MOOC de l&rsquo;ANSSI m&rsquo;a offert une opportunit\u00e9 pr\u00e9cieuse d&rsquo;approfondir mes connaissances en mati\u00e8re de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 informatique et de renforcer mes comp\u00e9tences dans la protection des syst\u00e8mes d&rsquo;information contre les cybermenaces. Ce programme m&rsquo;a permis de comprendre les principaux concepts et techniques de s\u00e9curit\u00e9, ainsi que les bonnes pratiques \u00e0 adopter pour garantir la s\u00fbret\u00e9 et la r\u00e9silience des infrastructures num\u00e9riques.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-constrained wp-block-column-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"border-width:5px;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignwide size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/MMOC_ANSSI_Romain_NGUYEN.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"301\" height=\"167\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_210151515.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-819\"\/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">(Cliquez sur l\u2019image pour le certificat)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;border-radius:0px;box-shadow:none\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp);flex-basis:800px\">\n<h1>Attestation <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">ATELIER RGPD DE LA CNIL<\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>J&rsquo;ai obtenu avec succ\u00e8s l&rsquo;attestation de participation \u00e0 l&rsquo;atelier RGPD de la CNIL, renfor\u00e7ant ainsi ma compr\u00e9hension des principes et des bonnes pratiques en mati\u00e8re de protection des donn\u00e9es personnelles.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-constrained wp-block-column-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"border-width:5px;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Attestation_de_suivie_CNIL_Romain_NGUYEN.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_210545208.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-831\" style=\"width:326px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_210545208.png 1024w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_210545208-300x156.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_210545208-768x400.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">(Cliquez sur l\u2019image pour le certificat)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-4 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;border-radius:0px;box-shadow:none\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp);flex-basis:800px\">\n<h1>Attestation\u00a0<span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">Cisco Networking Essentials<\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Cette certification atteste l&rsquo;obtention des comp\u00e9tences basiques fond\u00e9es sur le r\u00e9seau et de l&rsquo;informatique. Elle permet d&rsquo;apprendre les notions li\u00e9es au routeur, switch, pare-feu.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-constrained wp-block-column-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"border-width:5px;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/RomainNGUYEN-Networking-Essen-certificate.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"850\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_210022611.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-815\" style=\"object-fit:cover;width:325px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_210022611.png 850w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_210022611-300x176.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_210022611-768x452.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">(Cliquez sur l\u2019image pour le certificat)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp);flex-basis:800px\">\n<h1>Attestation <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">CCNA1<\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>J&rsquo;ai compl\u00e9t\u00e9 avec succ\u00e8s le CCNA 1 de Cisco, acqu\u00e9rant ainsi une compr\u00e9hension approfondie des fondamentaux des r\u00e9seaux informatiques, renfor\u00e7ant ainsi mes comp\u00e9tences et ma passion pour les technologies de l&rsquo;information et de la communication.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/RomainNGUYEN-CCNA1-Introduct-certificate.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"275\" height=\"183\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_205722564.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-809\"\/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">(Cliquez sur l\u2019image pour le certificat)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-6 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp);flex-basis:800px\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Attestation&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">CYBEROPS<\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>J&rsquo;ai obtenu la certification Cisco CyberOps, ce qui d\u00e9montre mon expertise approfondie en mati\u00e8re de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 des op\u00e9rations r\u00e9seau et m&rsquo;ouvre des opportunit\u00e9s professionnelles avanc\u00e9es dans le domaine de la cybers\u00e9curit\u00e9.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/RomainNGUYEN-2023-SIO2-CyberO-certificateSign.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image_2024-05-28_001210511.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-940\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image_2024-05-28_001210511.png 225w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image_2024-05-28_001210511-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">(Cliquez sur l\u2019image pour le certificat)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp);flex-basis:800px\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Attestation&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">TRY HACK ME<\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>J&rsquo;ai compl\u00e9t\u00e9 avec succ\u00e8s le parcours d&rsquo;apprentissage \u00ab\u00a0Introduction to Cyber Security\u00a0\u00bb de TryHackMe, acqu\u00e9rant ainsi une base solide de connaissances en s\u00e9curit\u00e9 informatique, et renfor\u00e7ant mes comp\u00e9tences dans la protection des syst\u00e8mes contre les cybermenaces.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/introduction-to-cyber-security-learning-path.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"742\" height=\"425\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_211741977.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-840\" style=\"width:322px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_211741977.png 742w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/image_2024-04-07_211741977-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 742px) 100vw, 742px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">(Cliquez sur l\u2019image pour le certificat)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-8 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp);flex-basis:800px\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Attestation\u00a0<span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">CAPGEMINI ACADEMY<\/span><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>J&rsquo;ai compl\u00e9t\u00e9 avec succ\u00e8s le parcours d&rsquo;apprentissage \u00ab\u00a0introduction forensic\u00a0\u00bb de CAPGemini lors de mon stage en cyber s\u00e9curit\u00e9, acqu\u00e9rant ainsi une base solide de connaissances en s\u00e9curit\u00e9 informatique, et renfor\u00e7ant mes comp\u00e9tences pratiques et th\u00e9oriques dans la protection des syst\u00e8mes contre les cybermenaces.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top has-border-color has-palette-color-2-border-color is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-967\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-6.png 225w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/image-6-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-697_610c48-01 .kt-block-spacer{height:6px;}.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-697_610c48-01 .kt-divider{border-top-width:5px;height:1px;border-top-color:#0083ff;width:84%;border-top-style:solid;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-spacer aligncenter kt-block-spacer-697_610c48-01\"><div class=\"kt-block-spacer kt-block-spacer-halign-center\"><hr class=\"kt-divider\"\/><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Mes certifications en <span style=\"color: #008000;\">Cours<\/span> ou <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">non r\u00e9alis\u00e9e<\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-column